---
title: Tofu and Black Bean Chipotle Chilli with peas and rice
description: As the name suggests, this is a meat-free take on the type of beef mince chillis typically favoured in firehouses across the US. Sitting on a bed of fluffy rice, this dish features tofu and an expert of spices.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R21_W29_IE_IECT23590-3_Main_high-f5b8b852.jpg
